ALICIA SEBERG, NATURALLY.

29:35.991 --> 29:38.907
BUT IT TURNS OUT SHE WASN'T
EVEN IN THE COUNTRY

29:38.907 --> 29:41.997
ON THE NIGHT IN QUESTION.WHO'S YOUR NEXT BEST GUESS?

29:41.997 --> 29:44.608
UM, THE ONE TIME I WENT
TO SEE CLIFF AT WORK,

29:44.608 --> 29:46.697
THERE WAS A LAB ASSISTANT.

29:46.697 --> 29:50.832
SHE GAVE ME THIS GLARE
LIKE A DEATH RAY,

29:50.832 --> 29:54.140
AND I THOUGHT MAYBE IT WAS HER.WHAT'S HER NAME?

29:54.140 --> 29:55.794
LILITH NASH.

29:55.794 --> 29:57.839
THE QUESTION IS WHY NOW?

29:57.839 --> 30:00.624
WHAT WAS IT THAT TRIGGERED
THE KILLING? WHAT CHANGED?

30:00.624 --> 30:03.018
WHAT'S THE ANSWER?

30:03.018 --> 30:06.543
[lowers voice] WELL, FOR
ONE THING, HARKEN SHOWED UP.YOU THINK HARKEN DID THIS?

30:06.543 --> 30:08.850
OOH, I'D LIKE THAT.
BUT WHAT'S HIS MOTIVE?

30:08.850 --> 30:10.765
[cell phone rings]

30:10.765 --> 30:12.158
VAN PELT.

30:12.158 --> 30:14.725
Boss, Cho and Rigsby found
an ex-lover

30:14.725 --> 30:16.205
of the vic's husband.

30:16.205 --> 30:18.947
SHE THINKS LILITH NASH SENT HER
A MENACING NOTE.

30:18.947 --> 30:22.081
INTERESTING.So I dug deeper.

30:22.081 --> 30:24.387
NASH IS CLEAN
UNDER HER CURRENT NAME

30:24.387 --> 30:27.695
BUT HAD A BRIEF MARRIAGE
IN CANADA IN '96, '97.

30:27.695 --> 30:30.916
Under that name, Lilith Blaum,
in '99, still in Canada,

30:30.916 --> 30:32.439
she had a restraining order
taken out against her

30:32.439 --> 30:34.963
BY HER EX-HUSBAND
AND SUBSEQUENTLY

30:34.963 --> 30:38.401
SPENT FOUR MONTHS
IN A SECURE MENTAL INSTITUTE.WELL, THAT COULD HAPPEN
TO ANYONE.

30:38.401 --> 30:40.229
UH, VAN PELT,
COULD YOU DO ME A FAVOR?

30:40.229 --> 30:42.318
COULD YOU CALL CHO AND RIGSBY
AND HAVE THEM GET OUT HERE

30:42.318 --> 30:44.016
AS QUICK AS POSSIBLE?WHY?

30:44.016 --> 30:46.409
I GOT A HUNCH
WE'RE GONNA NEED 'EM.OKAY.

30:46.409 --> 30:48.585
Thank you.WILL DO.

30:48.585 --> 30:50.674
LET'S GO TALK TO NASH.MEH.

30:50.674 --> 30:53.112
WHAT?
I THINK SHE'S GOOD FOR IT.AH, SHE'S NUTS.

30:53.112 --> 30:55.723
SHE'S GOT A NUTTY LITTLE
SECRET CRUSH ON THE BOSS,

30:55.723 --> 30:57.681
KILLS THE WIFE.SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

30:57.681 --> 31:00.119
SHE DID SEEM NERVOUS,
BUT WHY KILL NOW?

31:00.119 --> 31:03.296
AND WHY WOULD SHE USE
THE VIRUS?I DON'T KNOW.
LET'S GO AND ASK HER.

31:03.296 --> 31:05.080
UGH, IF YOU WANT TO.

31:05.080 --> 31:07.082
YOU KNOW,
YOU'RE JUST RESISTING NASH

31:07.082 --> 31:09.693
BECAUSE YOU DIDN'T PEG HER
RIGHT AWAY AS THE ONE.

31:09.693 --> 31:12.479
NO, I'M RESISTING NASH BECAUSE,
UH, SHE ISN'T THE ONE.

31:12.479 --> 31:14.829
BUT IF YOU WANNA GO TALK TO HER,
LET'S GO TALK TO HER.

31:14.829 --> 31:18.093
BUT WHATEVER YOU DO,
DO NOT TELL HARKEN.

31:18.093 --> 31:20.052
WHY NOT? IT'S PROCEDURE.

31:20.052 --> 31:22.445
FIG FOR PROCEDURE.
HE'LL STOMP ALL OVER HER.

31:22.445 --> 31:26.188
SHE'LL CLAM UP. YOU'LL GET
NOTHING BUT A WASTE OF TIME.I'M TELLING HARKEN.

31:26.188 --> 31:29.713
[sighs deeply]

31:29.713 --> 31:30.976
OKAY.

31:42.857 --> 31:44.685
[sighs]

31:46.469 --> 31:48.384
NASH, COME WITH ME.

31:49.864 --> 31:51.126
NOW.

31:58.742 --> 32:01.049
THANK YOU.

32:04.226 --> 32:05.836
STAND THERE.

32:05.836 --> 32:07.795
[door closes]

32:07.795 --> 32:09.057
[clank]

32:10.885 --> 32:14.541
LISTEN CLOSELY
AND PLEASE TELL THE TRUTH.

32:14.541 --> 32:17.848
IS THERE A WAY OUT OF HERE
THAT AVOIDS THE MAIN GATES?

32:17.848 --> 32:19.938
A BACK WAY OUT?YES.

32:19.938 --> 32:20.764
WHERE?

32:20.764 --> 32:22.244
WALK A MILE NORTH.

32:22.244 --> 32:24.855
THERE'S A CULVERT
THAT GOES UNDER THE FENCE

32:24.855 --> 32:27.075
HALFWAY ALONG
THE NORTHEAST PROPERTY LINE.

32:27.075 --> 32:30.296
EXCELLENT.
NOW... TELL THE TRUTH.

32:30.296 --> 32:33.603
DID YOU EVER GO
BY THE NAME LILITH BLAUM?

32:33.603 --> 32:35.040
YES.

32:35.040 --> 32:37.042
DID YOU SPEND TIME
IN A MENTAL ASYLUM?

32:37.042 --> 32:38.869
YES.

32:38.869 --> 32:42.308
DO YOU HAVE A SECRET CRUSH
ON CLIFF EDMUNDS?

32:42.308 --> 32:43.918
YES.

32:43.918 --> 32:46.268
DID YOU KILL ALICIA SEBERG?

32:46.268 --> 32:48.401
NO.

32:48.401 --> 32:50.011
I BELIEVE YOU,

32:50.011 --> 32:51.970
BUT I KNOW HOW
HARKEN'S THOUGHTS RUN.

32:51.970 --> 32:54.973
A WAY TO BLAME YOU
WILL BE FOUND.

32:54.973 --> 32:57.627
I REPEAT. I KNOW HOW
HARKEN'S THOUGHTS RUN.

32:57.627 --> 33:01.196
A WAY TO BLAME YOU
WILL BE FOUND. DO YOU HEAR ME?YES.

33:01.196 --> 33:02.981
EXCELLENT.

33:02.981 --> 33:04.025
[door opens]

33:07.898 --> 33:10.510
GO.

33:10.510 --> 33:12.164
[clears throat]

33:12.164 --> 33:13.469
[door opens]

33:13.469 --> 33:15.428
DID LILITH NASH
COME BACK IN HERE?

33:15.428 --> 33:16.995
NO.

33:16.995 --> 33:18.648
UH, THAT'S ODD.

33:18.648 --> 33:20.650
WHERE'S LILITH NASH?

33:20.650 --> 33:22.043
UH, SHE LEFT WITH--

33:22.043 --> 33:23.827
YOU DON'T NEED TO WORRY
ABOUT HER.

33:23.827 --> 33:25.699
SHE'S NOT GUILTY.

33:25.699 --> 33:28.789
AND HOW DO YOU KNOW THAT?BECAUSE I ASKED HER.
SHE TOLD ME.

33:28.789 --> 33:32.227
UH-HUH. AND WHERE IS SHE NOW?UM... I DON'T KNOW.

33:32.227 --> 33:33.533
SECURITY.

33:33.533 --> 33:35.361
[blinds rattle]

33:35.361 --> 33:38.233
[siren wailing]

33:44.935 --> 33:47.851
SHE'S NOT IN HER ROOM.
SHE'S NOWHERE TO BE FOUND.

33:47.851 --> 33:50.289
OH, YOU PEOPLE ARE OVERREACTING.
I'M SURE SHE'S NO DANGER.

33:50.289 --> 33:53.161
SHE'S MENTALLY UNSTABLE
AND PROBABLY A KILLER,

33:53.161 --> 33:56.338
BUT YOU'RE SURE SHE'S NO DANGER.
WELL, THAT'S REASSURING.WELL, EVEN IF SHE IS
THOSE THINGS,

33:56.338 --> 33:58.688
AND I DON'T SAY THAT SHE IS,

33:58.688 --> 34:01.648
THEN SHE'S DONE HER WORST
ALREADY.MR. HARKEN!
WE HAVE A CODE RED.

34:01.648 --> 34:04.433
WHAT'S A CODE RED?WHAT? NO.

34:11.788 --> 34:13.051
OH, NO.

34:14.791 --> 34:16.750
OH.

34:22.147 --> 34:24.540
ANYONE WITHIN A QUARTER-MILE
RADIUS OF THIS FLASK

34:24.540 --> 34:27.021
IS GONNA BE DEAD WITHIN
THE NEXT FOUR TO SIX HOURS.

34:27.021 --> 34:29.328
BUT I PUT THE FLASKS
IN THE SAFE.

34:29.328 --> 34:33.245
SHE MUST HAVE GOTTEN
INTO THE SAFE SOMEHOW.W-- H-HOW IS THAT POSSIBLE?

34:33.245 --> 34:36.117
[indistinct conversations]

34:50.610 --> 34:51.611
[click]

34:55.397 --> 34:57.356
WHAT WAS THAT?

34:57.356 --> 34:59.097
A BEAKER FELL.WHAT?

34:59.097 --> 35:03.057
THERE'S ONLY ONE MISSING.

35:03.057 --> 35:06.147
THAT'S A RELIEF, ANYHOW.
BUT HOW DID SHE DO IT?

35:06.147 --> 35:09.150
NEVER MIND HOW. SHE'S DONE IT.
WHAT DO WE DO NOW?

35:09.150 --> 35:11.152
WELL, THERE'S NOTHING
WE CANDO.

35:11.152 --> 35:13.981
IN THE NEXT FOUR HOURS,
WE'LL ALL BE DEAD.[latches click]

35:13.981 --> 35:15.939
[lowers voice]
TELL ME THE TRUTH.

35:15.939 --> 35:17.376
THIS IS A TRICK RIGHT?

35:17.376 --> 35:20.074
NO. WHY WOULD I DO
SOMETHING LIKE THAT?

35:20.074 --> 35:23.295
WHAT WOULD BE THE POINT?SWEAR ON YOUR CHILD'S GRAVE.

35:23.295 --> 35:26.124
YOU KNOW I DON'T DO THAT,
NOT FOR ANYTHING.

35:30.215 --> 35:33.218
OH, MY GOD.

35:33.218 --> 35:35.437
THIS IS A DRILL, RIGHT?UH, THIS IS NOT A DRILL.

35:35.437 --> 35:38.005
THIS IS--THIS IS THE REAL THING.
I'M SORRY.

35:38.005 --> 35:40.660
[all murmuring]

35:40.660 --> 35:43.663
LISTEN UP.

35:43.663 --> 35:46.361
WE HAVE A FEW HOURS LEFT.

35:46.361 --> 35:49.059
BUT WE'LL KEEP
THIS VIRUS CONTAINED HERE.

35:49.059 --> 35:52.106
NOBODY LEAVES THIS FACILITY.

35:52.106 --> 35:56.066
AND THEN WHAT?
WE GET BURIED IN THE DESERT?

35:56.066 --> 35:58.373
THE AIR FORCE WILL DROP
INCENDIARY BOMBS

35:58.373 --> 36:01.115
ON THE FACILITY,
BURN THE VIRUS OUT.

36:01.115 --> 36:03.378
YOUR NEXT OF KIN
WILL BE INFORMED.

36:03.378 --> 36:07.077
LIKE I SAY,
WE HAVE A FEW HOURS LEFT,

36:07.077 --> 36:09.645
SO WE ALL SHOULD MAKE
OUR ARRANGEMENTS

36:09.645 --> 36:12.344
AND SAY OUR PRAYERS
AS BEST WE CAN.

36:12.344 --> 36:14.433
MAKE YOUR PHONE CALLS.

36:15.912 --> 36:18.263
MAY GOD HAVE MERCY
ON OUR SOULS.

36:18.263 --> 36:23.006
[indistinct conversations]

36:23.006 --> 36:24.225
[speaking inaudibly]

36:29.012 --> 36:32.538
[cell phone rings]

36:32.538 --> 36:35.497
HEY, BOSS. WE'RE ABOUT
FIVE MINUTES FROM YOUR LOCATION.

36:35.497 --> 36:37.064
Cho, listen.

36:37.064 --> 36:39.893
JANE AND I HAVE BEEN EXPOSED
TO THE VIRUS,

36:39.893 --> 36:43.113
AND IT LOOKS LIKE
WE MIGHT DIE SOON.

36:43.113 --> 36:45.855
OKAY.

36:45.855 --> 36:50.120
SO I WANNA THANK YOU AND RIGSBY
AND VAN PELT.

36:50.120 --> 36:54.255
It's been an honor
working with you.

36:54.255 --> 36:56.605
I NEED YOU TO CALL
MY BROTHER TOMMY.

36:56.605 --> 36:58.607
HIS NUMBER IS
IN MY DESK DIARY.

36:58.607 --> 37:02.916
IT'S UNDER
TOWN AND COUNTRY ELECTRICAL.

37:02.916 --> 37:04.918
TELL HIM THAT I LOVE HIM

37:04.918 --> 37:07.877
AND THAT I FORGIVE HIM
FOR WHATEVER

37:07.877 --> 37:13.231
AND THAT, UM, HE NEEDS TO MAKE
PEACE WITH HIS BROTHERS.

37:13.231 --> 37:15.581
It's my last dying wish.
You tell him that.

37:15.581 --> 37:17.147
WILL DO.

37:17.147 --> 37:21.195
OKAY. GOOD-BYE.

37:21.195 --> 37:25.330
UH, WAIT. I-I WANTED
TO TALK TO THEM ALSO.

37:25.330 --> 37:26.635
SORRY.

37:26.635 --> 37:28.158
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

37:33.120 --> 37:34.817
THAT'S A FINE FAREWELL.

37:38.386 --> 37:42.216
I FEARED THAT YOU'D BECOME
TEARFUL AND INCOHERENT, BUT NO.

37:42.216 --> 37:44.784
SUCCINCT.

37:44.784 --> 37:47.134
NOBLE. BRAVO.

37:47.134 --> 37:49.049
UH-HUH.

37:51.530 --> 37:53.923
DON'T YOU HAVE ANYBODY
YOU WANNA CALL

37:53.923 --> 37:55.882
BESIDES CHO AND RIGSBY?

37:55.882 --> 37:57.275
NO.

37:59.581 --> 38:01.801
AND IF I WEREDYING,
I'D WANNA CALL YOU,

38:01.801 --> 38:04.630
BUT... YOU'RE ALREADY HERE.
SO THERE'S NO NEED.

38:04.630 --> 38:05.631
ME?

38:05.631 --> 38:07.067
HMM?

38:07.067 --> 38:08.503
WHAT WOULD YOU SAY?

38:08.503 --> 38:11.811
OH...

38:11.811 --> 38:16.555
UH... WAIT--
WAIT A MINUTE. IF?

38:18.861 --> 38:21.864
IFI WAS DYING?YEAH, YOU'RE NOT REALLY DYING.

38:21.864 --> 38:25.085
I WROTE A LABEL
AND PUT IT ON AN EMPTY FLASK,

38:25.085 --> 38:27.174
AND THEN I CONVINCED
POOR LILITH NASH TO RUN AWAY.

38:27.174 --> 38:30.308
I FEEL KIND OF BAD ABOUT IT--YOU SON OF A BITCH.

38:30.308 --> 38:33.006
BUT JUST--JUST WAIT.
JUST PLEASE. BE STILL. CHO?

38:33.006 --> 38:35.400
THIS IS JANE. PLEASE DISREGARD
LISBON'S LAST MESSAGE.

38:35.400 --> 38:37.967
I TRICKED HER. MY BAD.
[whispers] I'M SO SORRY.

38:37.967 --> 38:41.101
[normal voice] ARE YOU AT
THE CULVERT? OKAY, GOOD. WAIT.

38:41.101 --> 38:43.843
THERE'LL BE SOME PEOPLE
COMING YOUR WAY SOON. BYE.

38:43.843 --> 38:45.584
YOU'RE SICK.

38:45.584 --> 38:48.238
WHY WOULD YOU DO THIS
TO ME?

38:48.238 --> 38:51.241
TWO REASONS--FIRSTLY, TO CATCH
THE KILLER OF ALICIA SEBERG,

38:51.241 --> 38:53.505
THE KILLER WHO IS NOT
POOR LILITH NASH.

38:53.505 --> 38:55.724
THE KILLER WHO,
YOU MAY RECALL,

38:55.724 --> 38:58.510
TOOK A DOSE OF THE ANTIDOTE
IN ORDER TO SURVIVE

38:58.510 --> 39:00.512
EXPOSURE TO THE VIRUS. YES?YES...

39:00.512 --> 39:02.340
THE KILLER WHO BELIEVES
THAT HE OR SHE

39:02.340 --> 39:05.343
IS THE ONLY ONE
THAT ISN'T GOING TO DIE. YES?YES.

39:05.343 --> 39:08.128
SO THEY HAVE TO GET OUT OF HERE
BEFORE WEDIE,

39:08.128 --> 39:11.131
OR ELSE THEY'LL BE BURNT
TO A CRISP BY THE AIR FORCE.

39:11.131 --> 39:14.134
THEIR HANDS ARE TIED.
THEY HAVE TO TRY TO ESCAPE,

39:14.134 --> 39:16.789
THUS REVEALING THEMSELVES TO US
WITH PRECISION AND CLARITY

39:16.789 --> 39:20.401
OF A MATHEMATICAL EQUATION.AND REASON NUMBER TWO?

39:20.401 --> 39:22.403
THE SECOND
AND MOST IMPORTANT REASON

39:22.403 --> 39:26.581
IS DOESN'T IT FEEL GREAT
TO GET YOUR LIFE BACK?

39:26.581 --> 39:28.583
DON'T YOU FEEL GOOD
RIGHT NOW?

39:28.583 --> 39:30.803
DON'T YOU FEEL HAPPY
TO BE ALIVE?

39:30.803 --> 39:32.021
NO!

39:32.021 --> 39:34.154
OH, I KNOW YOU DO.
YOU KNOW YOU DO.

39:34.154 --> 39:37.331
IF REASON NUMBER ONE DOES NOT
PAN OUT VERY, VERY SOON,

39:37.331 --> 39:40.465
I THINK I'M GONNA PUNCH YOU
IN THE NOSE.

39:40.465 --> 39:42.162
FORBEARANCE, LISBON.

39:42.162 --> 39:44.773
ANY MOMENT NOW, HARKEN IS
GONNA COME AROUND THAT CORNER

39:44.773 --> 39:47.297
WITH AN ANXIOUS EXPRESSION
ON HIS FACE

39:47.297 --> 39:49.299
BECAUSE SOMEONE HAS RUN OFF.

39:49.299 --> 39:51.040
ANY MOMENT NOW.

39:51.040 --> 39:53.695
WAIT.

39:53.695 --> 39:57.046
ANY MOMENT.

39:57.046 --> 40:00.093
[sighs]

40:00.093 --> 40:01.268
NOTHING.

40:04.358 --> 40:06.012
IF YOU JUST GET--

40:06.012 --> 40:08.144
[whack]OW!

40:08.144 --> 40:11.147
OW!

40:11.147 --> 40:15.195
[Patrick] OW. WHOO!

40:15.195 --> 40:17.327
[high-pitched voice] THAT'S WHAT
I'M TALKING 'BOUT.

40:38.348 --> 40:40.133
HI.

40:46.052 --> 40:48.794
WELL, THIS WAS ALL A HOAX?

40:48.794 --> 40:52.493
WELL, "HOAX" IS A LITTLE STRONG.
UH, MORE OF A RUSE, A GAMBIT.

40:52.493 --> 40:55.148
THE IMPORTANT THING IS
WE CAUGHT THE KILLER.

40:55.148 --> 40:58.281
RIGHT? THAT'S WHAT'S IMPORTANT.THAT'S WHAT'S IMPORTANT.
GRIFFIN WELKS, HUH?

40:58.281 --> 41:01.023
NEVER WOULD HAVE CAUGHT HIM
YOUR WAY, AND MY WAY--

41:01.023 --> 41:03.112
CATHARTIC
ANDLIFE-AFFIRMING.

41:03.112 --> 41:07.203
YOU KNOW WHAT?
YOU'RE ON YOUR OWN.

41:07.203 --> 41:09.858
OKAY, THE IMPORTANT THING NOW
IS TO BE CAREFUL

41:09.858 --> 41:12.774
'CAUSE THIS IS
THE REAL THING. OKAY?

41:12.774 --> 41:15.211
ALL RIGHT, LET'S GET THAT BACK
IN THE DEEP FREEZE.

41:15.211 --> 41:17.562
SEE YOU AROUND, BIG DOG.

41:17.562 --> 41:19.520
[door opens]

41:25.091 --> 41:28.224
I WAS SIPHONING OFF SMALL
AMOUNTS OF THE VIRUS MATRIX

41:28.224 --> 41:30.183
AND SELLING IT
ON THE BLACK MARKET.

41:30.183 --> 41:31.619
$300,000 A GRAM.

41:31.619 --> 41:34.317
YEAH.

41:34.317 --> 41:36.102
YEAH, EXACTLY.

41:36.102 --> 41:39.192
I'M IN CHARGE OF KEEPING
INVENTORY, SO IT WAS EASY,

41:39.192 --> 41:41.542
UNTIL HARKEN ARRIVED
TO DO A SPOT CHECK,

41:41.542 --> 41:44.458
AND I HAD TO DO SOMETHING FAST,
SO I SPILLED A FLASK

41:44.458 --> 41:46.547
TO COVER UP
THE MISSING QUANTITY.

41:46.547 --> 41:49.115
KNOWING FULL WELL
ALICIA SEBERG WOULD BE EXPOSED.

41:51.073 --> 41:55.034
[sighs]
SOMEONE HAD TO BE RESPONSIBLE.

41:55.034 --> 41:57.645
I FIGURED
EVERYONE WOULD THINK

41:57.645 --> 41:59.604
THAT SHE'D OPENED THE FLASK
BY ACCIDENT

41:59.604 --> 42:01.867
AND COULDN'T ADMIT TO IT,

42:01.867 --> 42:04.870
'CAUSE SHE WAS LIKE THAT--
COULDN'T BE WRONG.

42:04.870 --> 42:09.048
I'M CURIOUS. THE MONEY
YOU MADE FROM YOUR THEFT--

42:09.048 --> 42:10.397
HOW'D YOU SPEND IT?

42:10.397 --> 42:12.225
I DIDN'T.

42:12.225 --> 42:14.662
I HAVE IT IN TREASURY BONDS
MOSTLY, SOME REAL ESTATE.

42:14.662 --> 42:16.664
MM-HMM,
THAT'S SMART INVESTING.

42:16.664 --> 42:18.536
YOU'LL BE THE RICHEST MAN
IN FOLSOM.

42:21.539 --> 42:24.150
[blinds rattle]

42:26.152 --> 42:29.111
[Patrick exhales deeply]

42:29.111 --> 42:30.896
WHEW. LONG DAY.

42:32.593 --> 42:34.160
OOH.

42:34.160 --> 42:36.902
IT'S CHILLY AROUND HERE.
YOU STILL ANGRY WITH ME?

42:36.902 --> 42:38.730
DUH.[elevator doors open]

42:38.730 --> 42:40.906
OH, CONFESS.
YOU DO FEEL BETTER.

42:40.906 --> 42:43.561
YOU FEEL MUCH MORE ALIVE.
I KNOW YOU DO.

42:43.561 --> 42:46.694
YOU KNOW WHAT
MADE ME FEEL BETTER?

42:46.694 --> 42:49.392
PUNCHING YOU IN THE NOSE.

42:49.392 --> 42:53.222
AH. GLAD TO BE OF SERVICE.

43:00.099 --> 43:03.058
STAY TUNED FOR SCENES
FROM OUR NEXT EPISODE.
